    "en": {
      "title": "Prime Minister starts work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena took office today (25th) at the Prime Minister's Office. Prime Minister's Secretary Mr. Anura Dissanayake, Prime Minister's Additional Secretary Mr. Harsha Wijewardene and other government officials as well as former Minister Namal Rajapaksa, former State Ministers Sisira Jayakodi, Arundika Fernando, Dr. Suren Raghavan, Members of Parliament Yadamini Gunawardena, Sagara Kariyawasam, Jagath Kumara, Manjula. Dissanayake and a group of people's representatives were also present."
      ],
